data.description: This move-in ready one story home with a large lot is located just minutes from MacDill Airforce Base in South Tampa. This home features 3 bedrooms 1.5 bathrooms 1,275 sqft of living space. As you walk in through the gorgeous blue front door, you'll be welcomed by a living space with laminate flooring that stretches throughout the home. Adjacent to the living space is a fully updated kitchen which is complete with gorgeous tall shaker cabinets, quartz countertop, stainless steel appliances, updated fixtures and lighting. Making your way to the lower level you'll step into a long radiant area perfectly suited for your dining space. This area offers great opportunity to enjoy home cooked dinners and spending time with family. Continuing on the lower level is a Florida like room filled wall to wall with gorgeous windows that look out to the luscious green back yard. This space offers an abundance of natural light and can be used an office . Making your way to the backyard you'll appreciate the spacious area the backyard has to offer. It is perfect for entertainment and fully fenced in. The backyard also includes a shed that will be great for storage. The roof is just 2 years old, partial updated plumbing, tankless water heater, an indoor laundry room and new windows makes this a great home. This house is a must see, schedule your tour today! No HOA. Close proximity to highways, shopping, restaurants and schools.
